<script>
jQuery(document).ready(function(){

	jQuery( window ).on( 'elementor/frontend/init', () => {
	
		var i=1;
		jQuery(".portfolio_left_area").find("h4.elementor-heading-title").each(function(){
			jQuery(this).addClass("port_btn");
			jQuery(this).addClass("port_btn_"+i);
			jQuery(this).data("actn",i);
			i++;
		});
		console.log("Total Btns:"+i);

		var j=1;

		jQuery(".portfolio_right_area").find(".elementor-inner-section").each(function(){
			jQuery(this).addClass("port_area");
			jQuery(this).addClass("port_area_"+j);
			j++;
		});

		console.log("Total Btn areas:"+i);

		hidearea(1);
		
		jQuery(".port_btn").click(function(e){
			e.preventDefault();
			
			var actn = jQuery(this).data("actn");
			console.log(actn);
			
			hidearea(actn);			
		});
		
		
	});
});
	
function hidearea(actn) {
	jQuery(".port_area").css("position","absolute");
	jQuery(".port_area").css("left","-10000px");
	
	jQuery(".port_area_"+actn).css("position","relative");	
	jQuery(".port_area_"+actn).css("left","0px");	
	
	jQuery(".port_btn.active").removeClass("active");
	jQuery(".port_btn_"+actn).addClass("active");
	
	console.log(actn);

}
</script>

<style>
	a, a:active, a:focus{
		outline: none;
	}
	.portfolio_left_area h4 a {
		display:block;
		padding: 6px 0 6px 15px !important;
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 16px !important;
	}
	.portfolio_left_area h4 a:hover, .portfolio_left_area h4.active a, .portfolio_left_area .port_btn.active h4 a{
		display:block;
	    color: #16CC8E;
		background-color: #f5f5f5;
	}
</style>
